data.description: Totally updated large garden home set in a cul de sac.  Zero carpet in this home as there are beautiful, hardy luxury vinyl planks.  Wonderful layout with all the space and updates.  The kitchen has upgraded cabinets, FARMHOUSE sink, Built in butlers pantry, gas stove and upgraded appliances.  Master suite will amaze you with the over the top upgrades for floors, vanity, molding and space.  Large dining room is open to the living room.  NEW ROOF, Huge open deck spans the length of the home overlooking natural land with very little yard to care for.  This home is perfect for the busy professional, traveling retiree, those who are allergic to major yard work and suits those who love to relax on the large deck listening to nature sing its song to you.  Curb appeal is maxed out here with the STACKED STONE entrance.
